Pedro is not only an amazing cobbler but truly a trustworthy and dependable guy. I just moved to London and was very nervous to use a new cobbler. I truly believe I got lucky finding Pedro. He fixed 3... Continue reading Pedro is not only an amazing cobbler but truly a trustworthy and dependable guy. I just moved to London and was very nervous to use a new cobbler. I truly believe I got lucky finding Pedro. He fixed 3 pairs of shoes within a few days. The shoes came out perfect. One pair of boots I brought in were so destroyed - especially on the inside but they came out looking better than ever. He had put in a beautiful leather to match the outside of my boots. He also recommended putting a small patch on the soles of my shoes to prevent the tips from getting ruined easily. I cannot be more grateful for your hard work and very fair prices.

Absolutely terrible service. Nobody sat us or even greeted us when we walked in. We sat at the counter, and after 10mins we had to ask for a menu. After another 8 we had to ask for water since nobody... Continue reading Absolutely terrible service. Nobody sat us or even greeted us when we walked in. We sat at the counter, and after 10mins we had to ask for a menu. After another 8 we had to ask for water since nobody brought us any. 30 mins total and again we had to ask to order. We weren't told what items they did not have up front, so we were disappointed when the drink we wanted wasn't available. The margaritas were super watered down and far too sweet. The fries had barely any flavor. Surprisingly the Cesar Salad was the only redeeming part. Nobody cleaned our area while we sat. Only when we were ready to pay. And they ended up taking my drink when there was still a few sips in there. Horrendous.

We weren't told what items they did not have up front, so we were disappointed when the drink we wanted wasn't available. The margaritas were super watered down and far too sweet.

The fries had barely any flavor. Surprisingly the Cesar Salad was the only redeeming part.

Nobody cleaned our area while we sat.  Only when we were ready to pay.  And they ended up taking my drink when there was still a few sips in there.  Horrendous.
